Quannah Rose Chasinghorse-Potts (amụrụ na June 6, 2002) bụ onye American Indian na-eme ihe nlereanya na onye na-echebe ala
Ọ pụtara na 2020 Teen Vogue ndepụta nke Top 21 under 21.

A mụrụ ya na mpaghara Navajo Nation na Tuba City, Arizona ebe nne ya na-agụ akwụkwọ n'oge ahụ, Chasinghorse bụ Hän Gwichńin nke Eagle Village, Alaska, n'akụkụ nne ya na Sicangu-Oglala Lakota nke Rosebud Indian Reservation na South Dakota n'akụkụ nna ya

Chasinghorce nọrọ n'oge ọ bụ nwata na Arizona, Mongolia, na New Mexico tupu ọ laghachi n'ala nna ya na Alaska mgbe ọ dị afọ isii. Ọ biri na Kenny Lake na Fairbanks. Ọ gara ụlọ akwụkwọ Effie Kokrine Charter School.
Chasinghorse bụ onye nchebe ala nke ọgbọ nke anọ maka Arctic National Wildlife Refuge dị ka akụkụ nke Alaska Wilderness League
O kwuru na ya achọghị ka ọgbọ ndị na-abịa n'ọdịnihu nọgide na-alụ ọgụ
Mgbe ọ dị afọ iri na asaa, ọ nọdụrụ na International Gwichīen Youth Council, na-aga Washington, D.C., New York, na Colorado
Ọ gbara mbọ megide ịgbazite mmanụ nke ga-emebi ebe mgbaba ahụ ma kwado HR 11-46, iwu nke ga-echebe ala ahụ kpamkpam
O sonyere na nzukọ ihu igwe ma na mpaghara ya ma na Denver
Ọ na-ekwu maka omume ihu igwe na ikike ụmụ amaala n'ọtụtụ ihe omume na ngalaba.

Chasinghorse nwere mmasị n'ịmepụta ihe na ejiji site na nwata mana, n'ihi enweghị nnọchiteanya ụmụ amaala ọ hụrụ na magazin na ihe ngosi ejiji, o cheghị na ọ ga-ekwe omume dị ka ọrụ. N'afọ 2020, ya na Calvin Klein mere ihe ngosi maka otu ọdịnihu ha #ckone youth campaign
Ọ bịanyere aka na IMG Models. Kemgbe ahụ, ọ pụtara n'ihu Vogue Mexico, Vogue Japan, V Magazine ma kọwaa ya na Vogue
Ọ ghọrọ onye a ma ama maka egbugbu ihu ya ọdịnala a na-akpọ Yidįłtoo.
Chasinghorse na-eme ka ọ bụrụ ihe na-eme emume ejiji ụmụ amaala na ịkwalite ụdị ụmụ amaala

Ọ na-ele anya na kapet na-acha ọbara ọbara na Gilded Age isiokwu Met Gala na Mee 2021 gbasara na mgbasa ozi mmekọrịta. Peter Dundas, Tabitha Simmons, Gucci Westman, na 2006 Miss Navajo Nation Jocelyn Billy-Upshaw, enyi ezinụlọ jikọtara uwe Navajo. Refinery29 kpọrọ ya "kpakpando" nke ihe omume ahụ. N'otu izu ahụ, ọ gara n'okporo ụzọ mbụ ya na New York Fashion Week.
